h2_title: Bishui Golden-Eyed Beast Boss Fight and Guide
content: Head up the stairs in this section and on the right, you'll be able to harvest a Fire Date. On the left, you can find an Awaken Wine Worm, and straight up ahead before the stairs, you'll see a green Wisp on the left.
